propClasses: Override or extend the styles applied to the component.
propComponent:
The component used for the root node.
Either a string to use a HTML element or a component.
propUnderline: Controls when the link should have an underline.
stylesRoot: Styles applied to the root element.
stylesUnderlineNone: Styles applied to the root element if `underline="none"`.
stylesUnderlineHover: Styles applied to the root element if `underline="hover"`.
stylesUnderlineAlways: Styles applied to the root element if `underline="always"`.
stylesButton: Styles applied to the root element if `component="button"`.
stylesFocusVisible: Pseudo-class applied to the root element if the link is keyboard focused.
